def test_jsonify_no_prettyprint(app, compact):
    app.json.compact = compact
    rv = app.json.response({"msg": {"submsg": "W00t"}, "msg2": "foobar"})
    data = rv.data.strip()
    assert (b" " not in data) is compact
    assert (b"\n" not in data) is compact
